2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses techniques to discover causal relations among observed variables in a given data set, which is a topic in artificial intelligence. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper uses information theory concepts such as entropy and mutual information to evaluate the performance of the proposed approach. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes a new causal model for binary data, which involves designing efficient data structures and algorithms.
